quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,49,"Ngakwembecheya ikaŵeje n’gumilo umpepe (lipenga lyandanda) wauchakwembekanya (mwachisupuchisya) aku ali nkukangana."
  36,50,"Basi ngasakombola kuleka wasiya, namuno kumaŵasa kwao ngasaujila."
  36,51,"Ni lichigombedwa lipenga (lyaŵili), basi papopo ŵanganyao kuumila m’malembe tachikopokangana mwachitemachitema wa kwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah)."
  37,34,"Chisimu Uwwe mwele ni mutukwatendelaga ŵakuleŵa."
  37,35,"Chisimu ŵanganyao ndema jakuŵechetedwa kukwao yanti: Pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Allah; ŵaliji nkulikwesya."
  37,36,"Ni kuŵechetaga yanti: “Ana chisimu uwwe tuleche milungu jetu ligongo lya nkwimba ilaanga, jwamasoka?”"
  38,13,"Kwisa soni Samuda, ŵandu ŵa Lutwi ni akutama nyyitekete (ŵandu ŵa Shuaibu). Jalakwejo ni mikutula (ja makafili jatwajijonasile)."
  38,14,"Pangali jwalijose mwa jamanjao ikaŵeje jwakaaniile Achimitenga, basi ni yasimichiche ipotesi Yangu."
  38,15,"Ni ngakwembecheya ŵanganyaŵa ikaŵeje n’gumilo umpepe (wa lipenga lya Kiyama) wangali kuusyaausya."